### Prerequisites

- [uv](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/) ≥ 0.5
- Python {{ python_version }} (managed by uv via `.python-version`)

### Common commands

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `make fix` | Auto-format and fix imports (run before committing) |
| `make check` | Full CI suite: format-check + lint + typecheck + tests |
| `make test` | Run tests only (faster) |
| `make typecheck` | pyright only |
